column3: Welcome, welcome! I am at your complete disposal as you venture forth into Eureka Orthos. I was given the honor of this appointment directly by Archmagus Noah, and I don't intend to let her down!
Are you sure you wish to enter with a fixed party?
Are you sure you wish to enter with a matched party?
You would brave Eureka Orthos alone!? Well, G'raha Tia and the archmagus have placed so much faith in you, and if they're not worried, I won't be─Allag's secrets are in your capable hands!
Are you sure you wish to enter alone?
From which floor will you enter?
Proceed to the next floor with your current party?
